  "detailed_description": "<strong>An idol making simulation game, Idol Queens!</strong><br><br>Produce your own idols in the way the real k-pop idols are produced!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>🔥 <strong>The most realistic idol making game</strong><br>Train your idols just like the real k-pop entertainment agencies do!<br>Be a producer, recruit and train trainees, and manage the agency as a business executive!<br>Expand your company internationally with your management strategy and produce a million-selling artist!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/32da36d3cc38a2b1e4ddc4e8edd0338d.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/32da36d3cc38a2b1e4ddc4e8edd0338d.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/32da36d3cc38a2b1e4ddc4e8edd0338d.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/db01fa42929ff7bee7dcd1d6e811c96c.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" wi